snippet.title: Willie Robertson Warns Atheists Jesus Is Coming

localized.description:
One of the Duck Dynasty duck call makers shot a promotional video for the upcoming Nicolas Cage movie about the Biblical End of Days in which he tells his fellow Christians to bring along their atheist friends to a screening in the hopes that they will be converted. Apparently, Cage’s acting is so good, a two hour movie can completely reverse a person’s belief system while they passively munch on buttered popcorn...

Read More At:
http://www.addictinginfo.org/2014/09/06/duck-dynasty-star-thinks-new-nicolas-cage-movie-will-convert-atheists/

Clip from the Friday, September 5th 2014 edition of The Kyle Kulinski Show, which airs live on Blog Talk Radio and Secular Talk Radio monday - friday 4-6pm Eastern.
